overview:
Content. Not Ads. Publishedin.com is the first marketing technology to use content instead of ads. With Publishedin AdFree network, advertisers get their content published on partner publishers’ websites, grow website traffic, leads and sales, improve search engine rankings and position their business as a thought leader.

Publishedin.com works with authentic voices from niche publishers with only one or two people delivering content to an audience of thousands, to the largest information, news or entertainment sites delivering content to an audience of millions. With Publishedin.com AdFree network, publishers deliver relevant and useful curated content to readers, while helping advertisers reach and engage with their target audience online.

Publishedin.com Publisher Network with more than 100,000 listed publishers in many categories, is the largest group of web publishers and bloggers leveraging content, audience and traffic to become more powerful than any other web property.

Publishedin’s patent-pending marketing solution is for any website owner and any type of business.
